*Stajao* je ispred zgrade i čekao (He was standing in front of the building and waiting).

Čovek se *stajao* da bi razgledao grad (The man stood up to take a look at the city).

On je *stajao* iza mene (He was standing behind me).

Mladić *stajao* je uspravno, bez pokreta (The young man stood still, without movement).

*Stajao* je tri sata u redu (He stood in line for three hours).